pages.title: React
pages.description: React is the library for web and native user interfaces. Build user interfaces out of individual pieces called components written in JavaScript. React is designed to let you seamlessly combine components written by independent people, teams, and organizations.
headings: Write components with code and markup
Add interactivity wherever you need it
Use the best from every platform
Upgrade when the future is ready
